Class OpenCollection<E>

java.lang.Object
craterdog.smart.SmartObject<Sequence<E>>
craterdog.collections.abstractions.Sequence<E>
craterdog.collections.abstractions.Collection<E>
craterdog.collections.abstractions.OpenCollection<E>
Type Parameters:
E - The type of element managed by the collection.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Composite<Sequence<E>>, Sequential<E>, Comparable<Sequence<E>>, Iterable<E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
OrderedCollection, SortableCollection
public abstract class OpenCollection<E> extends Collection<E>
This abstract class implements a collection that allows its internal structure to be directly manipulated.
Author:
Derk Norton
